title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (22): Machine Reading w/ Neural Nets
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Machine Reading
* Attention-based Machine Reading Models
* Multi-hop Reasoning Models

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-22-machinereading.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/yq5YuZ_QCxU
Next Video: https://youtu.be/oMB24_ao05A

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
